text: Asghar Zoghian (born 7 November 1929) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman welterweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
